blackout on the progress of the flight unless there was a major 
problem only two announcements were planned one about three hours 
after liftoff that orbital operations had begun and another 30 
hours into the flight with the date and time of landing 
atlantis and its crew of five military officers headed on a 
northeast course skirting the east coast 
