month was 96200 up 4 percent from december and 71 percent from 
january 1989 the median means half of the homes cost more half 
less 
the south was the only region posting an increase in sales in 
january up 07 percent to 140 million units the median price 
there was 86300 
the biggest decline in sales was in the west where the 
540000unit pace was 115 percent below the december rate the 
median price was 144000 up 7 percent from january 1989 but a 
