opponents has said he would sign whatever abortion legislation 
reached his desk if it were approved of by both house and senate 
democratic leaders 
but democratic leaders are split on the issue 
the measure would allow abortions only in these cases 
rape reported to police within 48 hours of the attack 
incest reported to authorities before the abortion 
pregnancy that threatens the womans life or endangers her 
health 
pregnancy that would result in a child born with profound 
and iremediable physical or mental disabilities incompatible with 
sustained survival 
it also would establish a system of civil penalties for those 
performing abortions and would set out requirements for informing 
pregnant women about the consequences of abortion 
