<TEXT>
paytelevision outlets would grab more sports 
programming from broadcast tv some magazines would have to close 
and thousands of media jobs would be lost if tobacco and alcohol 
advertising were outlawed a new report by an advertiser and media 
group says 
but critics said the report failed to reflect the chance that 
other advertisers would fill the void left by the tobacco and 
